  "local_port": 43554,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Where can I found a large range of formal and evening wear in Gold Coast?",
  "response": "If you're looking for a large range of formal and evening wear on the Gold Coast, here are some top recommendations where you can find a variety of options:\n\n1. **Pacific Fair Shopping Centre**\n   Located in Broadbeach, Pacific Fair is one of the largest shopping centers on the Gold Coast. It offers a wide range of stores catering to formal and evening wear, including:\n   - **David Jones**: Known for its extensive range of designer and formal wear.\n   - **Myer**: Offers a good selection of formal dresses and suits.\n   - **Zara** and **H&M**: Great for more affordable options in formal attire.\n   - **Specialty Boutiques**: Stores like **Forever New** and **Portmans** also offer a variety of evening and formal wear.\n\n2. **The Strand at Coolangatta**\n   This shopping centre, located in Coolangatta, has a few stores that stock formal wear:\n   - **Target** and **Kmart**: While not as upscale, they can offer affordable formal wear options.\n   - **City Beach**: Good for trendy and youthful formal wear.\n\n3. **Robina Town Centre**\n   Another large shopping complex on the Gold Coast, Robina has a variety of stores:\n   - **David Jones** and **Myer**: Similar to Pacific Fair, they offer a wide range of formal and evening wear.\n   - **Zara**, **H&M**, and **Uniqlo**: These stores often have sections dedicated to formal attire.\n   - **Specialty Boutiques**: Look for stores like **Seed Heritage** and **Country Road** for more formal options.\n\n4. **Harbour Town Premium Outlets**\n   Located in Biggera Waters, Harbour Town is great for finding formal wear at discounted prices:\n   - **Calvin Klein**, **Tommy Hilfiger**, and **Polo Ralph Lauren**: These stores often have formal wear sections with great deals.\n   - **Specialty Stores**: Keep an eye out for seasonal sales on formal attire.\n\n5. **Specialty Boutiques and Bridal Stores**\n   For more exclusive and high-end options, consider visiting specialty boutiques and bridal stores around the Gold Coast:\n   - **Luna & Soul**: Located in Burleigh Heads, they specialize in luxury formal wear.\n   - **Love Honor**: In Benowa, they offer a range of formal and evening dresses.\n   - **Velani**: Situated in Broadbeach, Velani provides elegant formal wear.\n\n6. **Online Shopping with Local Pickup**\n   Many stores on the Gold Coast offer online shopping with the option for local pickup or delivery:\n   - **The Iconic**, **ASOS**, and **Net-a-Porter** often have partnerships with local stores for easy pickup.\n\nBy visiting these locations, you should be able to find a wide range of formal and evening wear options to suit your needs on the Gold Coast. Enjoy your shopping!",
